  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You whisper a deadly song, as your victim enters a state of drowsiness. Choose one creature you can see within range, it must make a intelligence saving throw at the start of each of its turns.</p><p>A creature that fails this saving throw once, becomes slowed for the duration. And gains an additional rank of slowed each time it fails this save.</p><p>A creature that fails this save 3 times, becomes weakened and dazed for the duration.</p><p>A creature that fails this save 5 times, becomes unconscious until awakened by a <strong>restorative</strong> or similar jutsu of A-rank or higher, that can heal mental conditions.</p><p>A creature that suceeds their saving throw 3 times, end this jutsu on itself and becomes immune to it for the next 24 houts.</p>",
